catalogEntry.description:
NLog is a logging platform for .NET with rich log routing and management capabilities.
NLog supports traditional logging, structured logging and the combination of both.

Supported platforms:

- .NET Framework 3.5, 4, 4.5, 4.6, 4.7 & 4.8
- .NET Standard 1.3+ and 2.0+;
- .NET Framework 4 client profile
- Xamarin Android, Xamarin iOs
- UWP
- Windows Phone 8
- Silverlight 4 and 5
- Mono 4

For ASP.NET Core, check: https://www.nuget.org/packages/NLog.Web.Asp.NET Core

catalogEntry.description: NLog is a logging platform for .NET with rich log routing and management capabilities. It can help you produce and manage high-quality logs for your application regardless of its size or complexity. This package installs NLog.dll with includes core logging functionality. For your main project also need to install 'NLog Configuration' package.
catalogEntry.summary: NLog - Flexible & free open-source logging for .NET
